{"id":231786465,"title":"摩卡壺適用爐具","content":"大家好，第一次發文不知道有沒有錯版，再麻煩指正\n如題，BIALETTI的摩卡壺是鋁合金屬的材質，\n說明上是寫是用瓦斯爐、電爐、電陶爐，\n但不適用電磁爐、微波爐等，\n所以我想請問那種有同心圓金屬面板的電火鍋，可以拿來加熱摩卡壺嗎，怕買了結果不能用，因為宿舍也不能用瓦斯爐(怕危險)\n我的是這個，鍋子可拆\nhttps://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.png\n\n底下加熱的長這個\nhttps://i.imgur.com/CnHclCu.png\n\n我有找了資料，\n-電爐的原理如下：利用電熱管或電熱絲兩端通電後產生紅色火焰使爐面加熱，因此不必挑鍋\n\n-電磁爐的原理如下：電子線路震盪經由線圈產生高周波磁力線穿透陶瓷板使金屬鍋底直接發熱，選用鍋具時必須選擇金屬鍋底\n\n但實在不確定我的鍋子是哪種類型，所以發上來問問TT\n如果有錯版請告知謝謝！","excerpt":"大家好，第一次發文不知道有沒有錯版，再麻煩指正，如題，BIALETTI的摩卡壺是鋁合金屬的材質，說明上是寫是用瓦斯爐、電爐、電陶爐，但不適用電磁爐、微波爐等，所以我想請問那種有同心圓金屬面板的電火鍋，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["問題","摩卡壺","爐具"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"長庚科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.png"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/CnHclCu.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6b8deb10-a43b-46d3-b926-b1fe7d4df571","url":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z"},{"id":"6b8deb10-a43b-46d3-b926-b1fe7d4df571","url":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.png","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.png","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kwjHnCL.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-03T09:21:43.070Z"},{"id":"c1ea7e82-5